original_title: Taylor & Ultra: On the 60s, The Factory, and Being a Warhol Superstar
overview: Warhol Superstar Ultra Violet (Isabelle Colin Dufresne) and Lower East Side Icon Taylor Mead (Poet/Actor/Artist) share their stories of Manhattan in the 1960s.
title: Taylor & Ultra: On the 60s, The Factory, and Being a Warhol Superstar
